    • Customers

      public Customers(int customer_id, String customer_name, String address, String postal_code, String phone, LocalDate create_date, String created_by, Timestamp last_update, String last_updated, int division_id)
      Creates a new customer object with the specified parameters.
      Parameters:
      customer_id - The unique ID of the customer.
      customer_name - The name of the customer.
      address - The address of the customer.
      postal_code - The postal code of the customer.
      phone - The phone number of the customer.
      create_date - The date when the customer was created.
      created_by - The name of the user who created the customer.
      last_update - The timestamp when the customer was last updated.
      last_updated - The name of the user who last updated the customer.
      division_id - The ID of the division where the customer is located.
